title: Austin 'ActiveGuard' Powers PestWorld Invitation
text:
Austin 'ActiveGuard' Powers PestWorld Invitation Allergy Technologies invites attendees to its booth (#638) to meet Austin 'ActiveGuard' Powers. October 8, 2015 
The Allergy Technologies team looks forward to seeing pest management professionals at the upcoming PestWorld show in Nashville, Tenn.
